          "text": " is designed to retrieve invoice group and contract details from a SQL Server database. It takes several input parameters, some of which are optional, and returns a set of records from the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "vwInvoiceGroupContracts",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " view, joined with related data from "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "vwBillingGroups",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " and "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "vwProviders",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". The procedure also logs the operation details, including any exceptions, using another stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_AppLogCreate",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
